<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.DvtTigoMembership</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>false</client_callable><description/><name>DvtTigoMembership</name><script><![CDATA[var DvtTigoMembership = Class.create();
DvtTigoMembership.prototype = {
    initialize: function() {
        this.log = "";
    },

    /* ++++++++++++++++++++++++++ FUNCIONES DE CATALOGOS ++++++++++++++++++++++++++ */
    /* Función para obtener campos a partir de clave campus **/
    getCampus: function(claveCampus) {
        var campusId = "";
        var now_GR = new GlideRecord('cmn_location');
        now_GR.addQuery("u_clave_campus", "=", claveCampus);
        now_GR.query();
        if (now_GR.next()) campusId = now_GR.sys_id;
        this.log += "\n         >>> Ubicación obtenida = " + campusId;
        return campusId;
    },

    getMembershipType: function(membershipType) {
        var type = '';
        var now_GR = new GlideRecord('sys_choice');
        now_GR.addEncodedQuery("element=u_membership_type^name=u_membership^inactive=false^value=" + membershipType + "^ORlabel=" + membershipType);
        now_GR.query();
        if (now_GR.next()) type = now_GR.value;
        this.log += "\n         >>> Tipo de afiliación obtenida = " + type;
        return type;
    },

    /* Función para obtener campos a partir de clave campus **/
    getPerfilServicio: function(perfilesValue) {
        var perfilesId = new Array();
        var now_GR = new GlideRecord('u_service_profile');
        now_GR.addQuery("u_value", "IN", perfilesValue);
        now_GR.query();
        while (now_GR.next()) perfilesId.push(now_GR.getValue('sys_id'));
        this.log += "\n         >>> Ubicación obtenida = " + perfilesId.join(",");
        return perfilesId.join(",");
    },

    /* Función para obtener estatus de afiliación **/
    getAccountStatus: function(accountStatus) {
        var status = true;
        if (accountStatus == 0) status = false;

        return status;
    },

    getDomain: function(mailDomain) {
        if (gs.nil(mailDomain)) mailDomain = 'desconocido';
        return mailDomain;
    },

    /* Función para obtener institución a partir de dominio de correo **/
    getInstututionFromMaildomain: function(mailDomain, membershipType) {
        var institution = "desconocido";

        if (mailDomain == "@tec.mx" || mailDomain == "tec.mx" ||
            mailDomain == "@itesm.mx" || mailDomain == "itesm.mx" ||
            mailDomain == "@invitados.itesm.mx" || mailDomain == "invitados.itesm.mx" ||
            mailDomain == "@exatec.tec.mx" || mailDomain == "exatec.tec.mx" ||
            mailDomain == "sistematec.mx" || mailDomain == "pprd.exatec.tec.mx" ||
            mailDomain == "pprd.tec.mx")
            institution = "Tec de Monterrey";
        if (mailDomain == "@tecmilenio.mx" || mailDomain == "tecmilenio.mx" ||
            mailDomain == "@exa.tecmilenio.mx" || mailDomain == "exa.tecmilenio.mx" ||
            mailDomain == "pprd.tecmilenio.mx")
            institution = "Tecmilenio";
        if (mailDomain == "@tecsalud.mx" || mailDomain == "tecsalud.mx" ||
            mailDomain == "test.tecsalud.mx" ||
            mailDomain == "pprd.tecsalud.mx")
            institution = "Tec Salud";
        if (mailDomain == "@sorteostec.mx" || mailDomain == "sorteostec.mx" ||
            mailDomain == "test.sorteostec.mx" ||
            mailDomain == "pprd.sorteostec.mx")
            institution = "Sorteos";
        if (mailDomain == "arteac.edu.mx")
            institution = "Arte AC";
        if ((mailDomain == "" || mailDomain == null || mailDomain == "desconocido") && membershipType == 'PersonaRel')
            institution = "Tec de Monterrey";

        return institution;
    },

    getEmail: function(email) {
        if (gs.nil(email)) return '';

        var correoContacto = email.toString();
        var emailTrim = correoContacto.replace(/\s+/g, ',');
        var arrayCorreo = emailTrim.split(",");

        log = "\n" + "emailTrim = " + emailTrim;
        log += "\n" + "emailTrim.split(", ") = " + arrayCorreo;
        log += "\n" + "arrayCorreo[0] = " + arrayCorreo[0];
        //gs.info(log);

        return arrayCorreo[0];
    },

    getGraduationYears: function(graduatioDateString) {
        return graduatioDateString.replace(/ /g, ", ");
    },

    /* ++++++++++++++++++++++++++ FUNCIONES CRUD USUARIOS Y MEMEBERSHIP ++++++++++++++++++++++++++ */
    getUser: function(userName) {
        var userId = "";
        var now_GR = new GlideRecord('sys_user');
        now_GR.addQuery("user_name", "=", userName);
        now_GR.query();
        if (now_GR.next()) userId = now_GR.sys_id;

        this.log += "\n      >> User obtenido = " + userId;
        return userId;
    },

    insertUser: function(userName, firstName, lastName, secondLastName, mobilePhone) {
        var userId = '';
        var now_GR = new GlideRecord('sys_user');
        now_GR.initialize();
        now_GR.user_name = userName;
        now_GR.first_name = firstName;
        now_GR.last_name = lastName;
        now_GR.u_second_last_name = secondLastName;
        now_GR.mobile_phone = mobilePhone;
        userId = now_GR.insert();

        this.log += "\n      >> User insertado = " + userId;
        return userId;
    },

    updateUser: function(userName, firstName, lastName, secondLastName, mobilePhone) {
        var userId = '';
        var now_GR = new GlideRecord('sys_user');
        now_GR.addQuery("user_name", "=", userName);
        now_GR.query();
        if (now_GR.next()) {
            now_GR.user_name = userName;
            now_GR.first_name = firstName;
            now_GR.last_name = lastName;
            now_GR.u_second_last_name = secondLastName;
            now_GR.mobile_phone = mobilePhone;
            userId = now_GR.update();
        }

        this.log += "\n      >> User actualizado = " + userId;
        return userId;
    },

    saveUser: function(userName, firstName, lastName, secondLastName, mobilePhone) {
        var userId = '';

        var idUser = this.getUser(userName);
        if (gs.nil(idUser)) userId = this.insertUser(userName, firstName, lastName, secondLastName, mobilePhone);
        else {
            userId = this.updateUser(userName, firstName, lastName, secondLastName, mobilePhone);
            if (gs.nil(userId)) userId = idUser;
        }

        this.log += "\n      >> User final = " + userId;
        return userId;
    },

    getMembership: function(userNameId, membershipId, contactEmail) {
        var membership = "";
        var now_GR = new GlideRecord('u_membership');
        now_GR.addQuery("u_user", "=", userNameId);
        now_GR.addQuery("u_membership_id", "=", membershipId);
        if (!gs.nil(contactEmail)) now_GR.addQuery("u_contact_email", "=", contactEmail);
        now_GR.query();
        if (now_GR.next()) membership = now_GR.sys_id;

        this.log += "\n      >> Membership obtenido = " + membership + " | " + userNameId + " | " + membershipId;
        return membership;
    },

    insertMembership: function(userNameId, membershipId, membershipType, contactEmail, alternativeEmail,
        accountStatus, campusSede, claveMajor, academicProgramKey, academicPprogramDescription,
        gratuateStatus, institution, serviceProfile, mailDomain, academicRole, societyKey,
        societyDescription, divisionKey, divisionDescription, subdivisionKey, subdivisionDescription,
        academicLevel, dateGraduationString, activationStatus, recintofisico) {

        var membership = '';
        var now_GR = new GlideRecord('u_membership');
        now_GR.initialize();
        now_GR.u_user = userNameId;
        now_GR.u_membership_id = membershipId;
        now_GR.u_membership_type = this.getMembershipType(membershipType);
        now_GR.u_contact_email = this.getEmail(contactEmail);
        now_GR.u_alternative_email = this.getEmail(alternativeEmail);
        now_GR.u_account_status_string = accountStatus;
        //now_GR.u_account_status = this.getAccountStatus(accountStatus);
        now_GR.u_campus_sede = this.getCampus(campusSede);
        now_GR.u_clave_major = claveMajor;
        now_GR.u_academic_program_key = academicProgramKey;
        now_GR.u_academic_program_description = academicPprogramDescription;
        now_GR.u_gratuate_status = gratuateStatus;
        now_GR.u_service_profile = this.getPerfilServicio(serviceProfile);
        now_GR.u_mail_domain = this.getDomain(mailDomain);
        now_GR.u_institution = this.getInstututionFromMaildomain(now_GR.u_mail_domain, now_GR.u_membership_type);
        now_GR.u_academic_role = academicRole;
        now_GR.u_society_key = societyKey;
        now_GR.u_society_description = societyDescription;
        now_GR.u_division_key = divisionKey;
        now_GR.u_division_description = divisionDescription;
        now_GR.u_subdivision_key = subdivisionKey;
        now_GR.u_subdivision_description = subdivisionDescription;

        now_GR.u_academic_level = academicLevel;
        now_GR.u_date_graduation_string = this.getGraduationYears(dateGraduationString);
        now_GR.u_activation_status = this.getActivationStatus(activationStatus);
        /*start HU1168 */
        now_GR.u_recintofisico = recintofisico;
        now_GR.u_recinto_fisico_desc = this.getCampus(recintofisico); 
        /* end HU1168 */

        membership = now_GR.insert();

        this.log += "\n      >> Membership insertado = " + membership;
        return membership;
    },

    getActivationStatus: function(activationStatus) {
        var status = true;
        if (activationStatus == 'true' || activationStatus == true ||
            activationStatus == 'VERDADERO' || activationStatus == "TRUE") status = false;

        return activationStatus;
    },

    updateMembership: function(userNameId, membershipId, membershipType, contactEmail, alternativeEmail,
        accountStatus, campusSede, claveMajor, academicProgramKey, academicPprogramDescription,
        gratuateStatus, institution, serviceProfile, mailDomain, academicRole, societyKey,
        societyDescription, divisionKey, divisionDescription, subdivisionKey, subdivisionDescription,
        academicLevel, dateGraduationString, activationStatus, recintofisico) {

        var email = this.getEmail(contactEmail);
        var membership = '';
        var now_GR = new GlideRecord('u_membership');
        now_GR.addQuery("u_user", "=", userNameId);
        now_GR.addQuery("u_membership_id", "=", membershipId);
        if (!gs.nil(contactEmail)) now_GR.addQuery("u_contact_email", "=", email);
        now_GR.query();
        if (now_GR.next()) {
            //now_GR.u_user = userNameId;
            now_GR.u_membership_id = membershipId;
            now_GR.u_membership_type = this.getMembershipType(membershipType);
            now_GR.u_contact_email = this.getEmail(contactEmail);
            now_GR.u_alternative_email = this.getEmail(alternativeEmail);
            now_GR.u_account_status_string = accountStatus;
            //now_GR.u_account_status = this.getAccountStatus(accountStatus);
            now_GR.u_campus_sede = this.getCampus(campusSede);
            now_GR.u_clave_major = claveMajor;
            now_GR.u_academic_program_key = academicProgramKey;
            now_GR.u_academic_program_description = academicPprogramDescription;
            now_GR.u_gratuate_status = gratuateStatus;
            now_GR.u_service_profile = this.getPerfilServicio(serviceProfile);
            now_GR.u_mail_domain = this.getDomain(mailDomain);
            now_GR.u_institution = this.getInstututionFromMaildomain(now_GR.u_mail_domain, now_GR.u_membership_type);
            now_GR.u_academic_role = academicRole;
            now_GR.u_society_key = societyKey;
            now_GR.u_society_description = societyDescription;
            now_GR.u_division_key = divisionKey;
            now_GR.u_division_description = divisionDescription;
            now_GR.u_subdivision_key = subdivisionKey;
            now_GR.u_subdivision_description = subdivisionDescription;

            now_GR.u_academic_level = academicLevel;
            now_GR.u_date_graduation_string = this.getGraduationYears(dateGraduationString);
            now_GR.u_activation_status = this.getActivationStatus(activationStatus);

            /*start HU1168 */
            now_GR.u_recintofisico = recintofisico;
            now_GR.u_recinto_fisico_desc = this.getCampus(recintofisico); 
            /* end HU1168 */

            membership = now_GR.update();
        }

        this.log += "\n      >> Membership actualizado = " + membership;
        return membership;
    },

    saveMembership: function(userNameId, membershipId, membershipType, contactEmail, alternativeEmail,
        accountStatus, campusSede, claveMajor, academicProgramKey, academicPprogramDescription,
        gratuateStatus, institution, serviceProfile, mailDomain, academicRole, societyKey,
        societyDescription, divisionKey, divisionDescription, subdivisionKey, subdivisionDescription,
        academicLevel, dateGraduationString, activationStatus,  recinto_fisico) {
        var membership = '';
        var email = this.getEmail(contactEmail);

        var idMembership = this.getMembership(userNameId, membershipId, email);
        if (gs.nil(idMembership))
            membership = this.insertMembership(userNameId, membershipId, membershipType, contactEmail, alternativeEmail,
                accountStatus, campusSede, claveMajor, academicProgramKey, academicPprogramDescription,
                gratuateStatus, institution, serviceProfile, mailDomain, academicRole, societyKey,
                societyDescription, divisionKey, divisionDescription, subdivisionKey, subdivisionDescription,
                academicLevel, dateGraduationString, activationStatus,  recinto_fisico);
        else
            membership = this.updateMembership(userNameId, membershipId, membershipType, contactEmail, alternativeEmail,
                accountStatus, campusSede, claveMajor, academicProgramKey, academicPprogramDescription,
                gratuateStatus, institution, serviceProfile, mailDomain, academicRole, societyKey,
                societyDescription, divisionKey, divisionDescription, subdivisionKey, subdivisionDescription,
                academicLevel, dateGraduationString, activationStatus,  recinto_fisico);

        this.log += "\n      >> Membership final = " + membership;
        return membership;
    },

    /* Función para establecer el estado de cuenta de una afiliación **/
    setActiveMembership: function(idUser, active) {
        var membership = new GlideRecord('u_membership');
        membership.addQuery('u_user', '=', idUser);
        membership.query();
        while (membership.next()) {
            membership.u_account_status = active;
            membership.update();
            if (active == true) gs.addInfoMessage("Se Activan Afiliaciones por Activación de Usuario.");
            else gs.addInfoMessage("Se Desactivan Afiliaciones por Desactivación de Usuario.");
        }
    },

    /* Función para establecer el activo de un usuario **/
    setActiveUser: function(idUser, active) {
        var user = new GlideRecord('sys_user');
        var rc = user.get(idUser);
        if (rc) {
            if (user.active != active) {
                user.active = active;
                if (active == true) user.locked_out = false;
                user.update();
                if (active == true) gs.addInfoMessage("Se Activa Usuario por Activación de Afiliaciones.");
                else gs.addInfoMessage("Se Desactiva Usuario por Desactivación de Afiliaciones.");
            }
        }
    },

    /* ++++++++++++++++++++++++++ FUNCIONES DE PRINCIPALES ++++++++++++++++++++++++++ */
    /* Función para soportar aprovisionamiento a partir de un JSON enviado en la REST API **/
    addMemberShipJson: function(jsonRequest) {
        var log = "APROVISIONAMIENTO TEC";
        var userName = jsonRequest.user_name;
        var firstName = jsonRequest.first_name;
        var lastName = jsonRequest.last_name;
        var secondLastName = jsonRequest.u_second_last_name;
        var mobilePhone = jsonRequest.mobile_phone;
        var membershipId = jsonRequest.u_membership_id;
        var membershipType = jsonRequest.u_membership_type;
        var contactEmail = jsonRequest.u_contact_email;
        var alternativeEmail = jsonRequest.u_alternative_email;
        var accountStatus = jsonRequest.u_account_status;
        var campusSede = jsonRequest.u_campus_sede;
        var claveMajor = jsonRequest.u_clave_major;
        var academicProgramKey = jsonRequest.u_academic_program_key;
        var academicPprogramDescription = jsonRequest.u_academic_program_description;
        var gratuateStatus = jsonRequest.u_gratuate_status;
        var institution = jsonRequest.u_institution;
        var serviceProfile = jsonRequest.u_service_profile;
        var mailDomain = jsonRequest.u_mail_domain;
        var academicRole = jsonRequest.u_academic_role;
        var societyKey = jsonRequest.u_society_key;
        var societyDescription = jsonRequest.u_society_description;
        var divisionKey = jsonRequest.u_division_key;
        var divisionDescription = jsonRequest.u_division_description;
        var subdivisionKey = jsonRequest.u_subdivision_key;
        var subdivisionDescription = jsonRequest.u_subdivision_description;

        var academicLevel = jsonRequest.u_academic_level;
        var dateGraduationString = jsonRequest.u_date_graduation_string;
        var activationStatus = jsonRequest.u_activation_status;

        /*start HU1168 */
        var u_recinto_fisico= jsonRequest.u_recinto_fisico;
        /* end HU1168 */

        log += "\n" + "   > JSON = " + JSON.stringify(jsonRequest);
        this.log += log;

        var userNameId = this.saveUser(userName, firstName, lastName, secondLastName, mobilePhone);
        var membership = this.saveMembership(userNameId, membershipId, membershipType, contactEmail, alternativeEmail,
            accountStatus, campusSede, claveMajor, academicProgramKey, academicPprogramDescription,
            gratuateStatus, institution, serviceProfile, mailDomain, academicRole, societyKey,
            societyDescription, divisionKey, divisionDescription, subdivisionKey, subdivisionDescription, academicLevel, dateGraduationString, activationStatus,  u_recinto_fisico);

        gs.info(this.log);
        return (!gs.nil(userNameId) && !gs.nil(membership));
    },

    /** Función para activar usuarios a partir de afiliación activos */
    activeUserFromMembership: function(idUser) {
        var countAll = 0;
        var countOff = 0;
        var countOn = 0;

        //Obtener Afiliaciones activas
        var membership = new GlideRecord('u_membership');
        membership.addQuery('u_user', '=', idUser);
        membership.query();
        countAll = membership.getRowCount();
        while (membership.next()) {
            if (membership.getValue("u_account_status") == true) countOn++;
            if (membership.getValue("u_account_status") == false) countOff++;
        }

        if (countOn == 0 && countOff == countAll) this.setActiveUser(idUser, false);
        if (countOn > 0) this.setActiveUser(idUser, true);

        return;
    },

    /** Función para adicionar y elimianr los roles un usuario a partir de los registros de afiliación activos */
    addRolesFromMembership: function(idUser) {
        //Inicializar variables
        var roles = new Array();
        var rolesDelete = new Array();
        var rolesInsert = new Array();
        var prefijoRole = 'tecaprov_';
        var log = '   >> [addRolesFromMembership]';

        //Obtener Afiliaciones activas
        var membership = new GlideRecord('u_membership');
        membership.addQuery('u_user', '=', idUser);
        membership.addQuery('u_account_status', '=', true);
        membership.query();
        while (membership.next())
            if (roles.indexOf(membership.getValue('u_membership_type')) == -1)
                roles.push('tecaprov_' + membership.getValue('u_membership_type'));
        log += '\n     >>> Roles activos = ' + roles.length + ' [' + roles.join(', ') + ']';

        //Eliminar Roles de Afiliaciones sobrantes
        var userRoleDelete = new GlideRecord('sys_user_has_role');
        userRoleDelete.addQuery('user', '=', idUser);
        userRoleDelete.addQuery('role.name', 'STARTSWITH', prefijoRole);
        if (roles.length > 0) userRoleDelete.addEncodedQuery('role.name!=' + roles.join('^ORrole.name!='));
        userRoleDelete.query();
        while (userRoleDelete.next()) {
            rolesDelete.push(userRoleDelete.getDisplayValue('role'));
            gs.addInfoMessage(gs.getMessage("Removing Role {0} from {1}", [userRoleDelete.getDisplayValue('role'), userRoleDelete.getDisplayValue('user')]));
            userRoleDelete.deleteRecord();
        }
        log += '\n     >>> Roles eliminados = ' + rolesDelete.length + ' [' + rolesDelete.join(', ') + ']';

        if (roles.length <= 0) {
            gs.info(log);
            return;
        }

        //Adicionar Roles de Afiliaciones nuevos
        for (var i in roles) {
            var rol = roles[i];
            var userRoleCreate = new GlideRecord('sys_user_has_role');
            userRoleCreate.addQuery('user', '=', idUser);
            userRoleCreate.addQuery('role', '=', rol);
            userRoleCreate.query();
            if (!userRoleCreate.next()) {

                //Obtener rol
                var userRole = new GlideRecord('sys_user_role');
                userRole.addQuery('name', '=', rol);
                userRole.query();
                gs.info("Query Rol busca = " + userRole.getEncodedQuery());
                if (userRole.next()) {

                    //Insertar Role
                    var userRoleInsert = new GlideRecord('sys_user_has_role');
                    userRoleInsert.initialize();
                    userRoleInsert.user = idUser;
                    userRoleInsert.role = userRole.getValue('sys_id');
                    userRoleInsert.insert();
                    gs.addInfoMessage(gs.getMessage("Adding Role {0} to {1}", [userRoleInsert.getDisplayValue('role'), userRoleInsert.getDisplayValue('user')]));
                    rolesInsert.push(userRoleInsert.getDisplayValue('role'));
                }
            }
        }

        log += '\n     >>> Roles agregados = ' + rolesInsert.length + ' [' + rolesInsert.join(', ') + ']';
        gs.info(log);
        return;
    },

    type: 'DvtTigoMembership'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>DevDevoteam3</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2022-10-20 01:50:58</sys_created_on><sys_id>fb2dccdb47ae9d10676de567436d43e3</sys_id><sys_mod_count>62</sys_mod_count><sys_name>DvtTigoMembership</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_fb2dccdb47ae9d10676de567436d43e3</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>DevDevoteam4</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2023-10-13 19:47:46</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
